quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  23,105,"Enee, hara Aayeeje Am …óen laataaki no janngee e taweede mo'on, laati…óon ho…óon njedda …óe?"
  23,106,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Joomi amen, ko malkiso amen ngon foolii min, min laatinoke yim…ďe majju…ďe.""
  23,107,"Joomi amen, yaltin min e magge, si min ruttike hara pellet, minen ko min too√Ī…ďe."
  23,108,"O Daala: "√Ďii…ďee e ndeer magge wota on kaalanam"."
  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jiyaa…ďe Am …ďen hi…ďe mbi'a: "Joomi amen, min ngooŇč…óinii haforan men njurme∆äaa men ko Aan …ďuri Mo∆ī∆īude Yurmetee…ďe …ďeen"."
  23,110,"NJogiti…óon …ďe jalnori(jalkigol), haa …ďe njejjintini on jaŇčta Am, laati…óon ho…óon njala …ďe."
  23,111,"Min Mi yo…ďii …ďe hannde sabu ko …ďe mu√Ī√Īinoo kon, pellet, kam…ďe ko kam…ďe ngoni malaa…ďe …ďeen."
  23,112,"O Daali: "No foti heewde ko √Īii…ď…óon ka leydi, limoore duu…ďi?""
  23,113,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Min √Īii…ďii √Īallal maa…óum yoga e √Īallal, lanndo limoo…ďe …ďeen.""
  23,114,"O Daali: "On √Īii…ďaani si wonaa see…óa, sinndo onon on laatino ho…óon nganndi.""
  23,115,"Enee, on cikku wonan'dema ko Min Tagiri on ko puyndan, hara onon on mduttetaake fa'ade ka Amen?!"
  23,116,"Alla Toowii Laam…óo Goongu…óo On, dewetee- …óo alah si wonaa KaŇčko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin."
  23,117,"Kala noddu…óo wond'ude e Alla dewetee…óo goo, daliil alanah mo e …óum, anndu pellet, hasboo- re makko ko ka Joomi makko, pellet KaŇčko, O malnatah heefer…ďe …ďeen."
  23,118,"Maaku: "Jooma am, Yaafo Yurmo ko Aan ∆Āuri Mo∆ī∆īude Yurmetee…ďe …ďen.""